author: AP
title: Soccer team from Wuhan returns home nearly 4 months later
description: The soccer team based in the epicenter of the coronavirus pandemic in China has returned home
content:
MADRID (AP) — The soccer team based in the epicenter of the coronavirus pandemic in China is back home, nearly four months after it left for a preseason tour and got stuck abroad.
